description: Commit message suggestion at the end of every task
alwaysApply: true
---

At the end of every completed project-related task, always provide exactly one suggested git commit message.

Use Conventional Commits format.

Examples:
- `feat: add authentication flow`
- `fix: resolve navbar overflow on mobile`
- `refactor: simplify user service logic`
- `style: update dashboard layout`
- `docs: update setup instructions`
- `chore: update dependencies`

The commit message must:
- Be in English
- Be concise
- Describe the actual changes made
- Not end with a period

Always place it at the very end of the response in this format:

Commit message:
`type: short description`